videos.description: Duke shows their athleticism early leading to an easy score for Marvin Bagley III.
videos.headline: Bagley gets first bucket

videos.description: Marvin Bagley III gets out on the fast break and slams an easy two-hand flush.
videos.headline: Bagley throws it down

videos.description: Grayson Allen hits the three-pointer for his 15th point on 6-of-7 shooting in the first ten minutes of play.
videos.headline: Allen drains a three

videos.description: Marvin Bagley III runs the fast break to perfection and lays it in with the foul.
videos.headline: Bagley sinks the and-1 layup

videos.description: Grayson Allen makes an acrobatic layup as he goes crashing to the floor.
videos.headline: Allen goes coast-to-coast

videos.description: Trevon Duval gets a little too fancy as he ripped a nice pass straight out of bounds for the turnover.
videos.headline: Duke's Duval makes behind-the-back pass to no one

videos.description: Trevon Duval cuts through the lane and finishes with a smooth floater.
videos.headline: Duke's Duval sinks the lefty lay-in

videos.description: All five Blue Devils touch the ball to set up a powerful dunk for Wendell Carter Jr.
videos.headline: Carter throws it down for Duke
